Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Maintainer: Matthew Newton <mcn4@leicester.ac.uk>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8)

Package: log-courier
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Log file shipper
 Log Courier is a tool created to transmit log files speedily and securely to
 remote Logstash instances for processing whilst using small amounts of local
 resources. The project is an enhanced fork of Logstash Forwarder 0.3.1 with
 many enhancements and behavioural improvements.

Package: log-courier-gem
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, logstash (>= 1.4.0)
Description: Log file shipper collector
 Log Courier is a tool created to transmit log files speedily and securely to
 remote Logstash instances for processing whilst using small amounts of local
 resources. The project is an enhanced fork of Logstash Forwarder 0.3.1 with
 many enhancements and behavioural improvements.
 .
 This package contains the jruby gem and filters to receive shipped logs into
 logstash.

